USAGE INSTRUCTIONS:

1. Environment Variables (add to .env file):
   PUBLIC_GA4_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
   PUBLIC_GTM_ID=GTM-XXXXXXX
   PUBLIC_FACEBOOK_PIXEL_ID=123456789
   PUBLIC_HOTJAR_ID=1234567

2. Add to BaseLayout.astro:
   <Analytics />

3. Custom event tracking in your pages:
   <script>
     // Track button clicks
     document.getElementById('donate-button').addEventListener('click', () => {
       window.trackEvent('donate_button_click', { source: 'header' });
     });
     
     // Track newsletter signups
     window.trackEvent('newsletter_signup', { email: userEmail });
   </script>

4. Privacy Compliance:
   - Respects Do Not Track browser setting
   - Uses privacy-friendly GA4 settings
   - Anonymizes IP addresses
   - Secure cookie settings

